File -> New -> Other -> Maven -> Maven Project -> Next-> Next-> 
org.apache.maven.archetypes maven.archetypes.quickstart ->Next ->
Change Artifact Id to Maven project name.
Add dependancies in pom.xml by grabbing it from internet.
Right click project folder and hit Maven-> Update Project.
Change all Java files to end with *Test.java
Right click project folder and click properties and add M2_REPO in module path in Libraries.